----
No floating values for position:
AfterFx Expression
----
Author: GaragePixel
Date: 2023-11-05
----
Plot: Rounding a value on the Position variable
----
Usage: Put this script in the Position parameter of any layer.
1. Use ALT+click over the watch to link the parameter to the script and copy/paste this code
2. Add this by preference after making an key animation.
----
[Math.floor(transform.position[0]),Math.floor(transform.position[1])]
